", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999997512609607, \"rank\": 1.2835276439065334e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toComplex, the speculation started when an X user @henrylmcnamara tweeted that an NBC exec claimed the rapper gets paid $500 000 a day.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999799525234726, \"rank\": 1.6918794684852164e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sat next to an NBC exec at dinner, he said Snoop gets paid $500k a day plus expenses to be here promoting Olympics.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999799525234726, \"rank\": 1.6918794684852164e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From 'Gin and Juice' to a few million to be a celebrity at the Olympics-what a world,\\\" read the tweet.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The publication also reported that sports business reporter Darren Rovell then quote-tweeted the post also speculating that the figure sounds about right, as he thought it would be around $10 million (R185 million).\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darren_Rovell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Darren Rovell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darren_Rovell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Darren_Rovell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sounds about right.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone asked me how much Snoop was making.\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First number that came to mind was $10 million,\\\" he wrote.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the Olympics have not yet confirmed that this is in fact the amount the rapper is making.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg has also taken on the role of being a special NBC Olympics correspondent.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also the torchbearer during the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheGin and Juicehitmaker carried the Olympic flame through the streets of Saint-Denis - a suburb in Northern Paris.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg was joined by French actress Laetitia Casta and French rapper MC Solaar, along with others.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\"